<faculty_text>Ellen J. Langer</faculty_text>
<description>This course will examine psychological and physical health from the perspective of Positive Psychology. A major focus will be on mindfulness theory and its relationship to stress/coping; illness/wellness; decision-making; placebos. The medical model, the bio social model, and a unified mind/body model will be compared to examine their relationship to achieving resilience.</description>
<prerequisites>SLS 20 and at least one course from Psy 13, Psy 14, Psy 15, Psy 18, or SLS 15.</prerequisites>
